      "text": "I wasnt sure what she was - I talked to obtain",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "much information as I could - I became interested",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "when she said - Russia has a poison which she will",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "place in an atom bomb that will destroy not",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "one city but dozens of cities - so when I read of",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
